metadata.name: Happy Meowvocado Birthday Rizzle!
metadata.description: Happy Birthday Rizzle! Wishing you all the happiness, joy, and blessings the world can offer on your birthday. Birthdays come once a year, but best friends are once in a lifetime. I'm so happy to call you mine! I'm so proud of you and for all that you do. Here's to the world's greatest friend! Cheers!
